  "page": "Brude",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Archmaester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/50px-Archmaester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/75px-Archmaester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/100px-Archmaester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Archmaester</span><br />Brude</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Archmaester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/50px-Archmaester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/75px-Archmaester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ae/Archmaester.svg/100px-Archmaester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">The Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nthe shadow city of Sunspear</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Brude</b> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">archmaester</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brude&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Brude was born in the shadow city of <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>. He famously observed that <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> has more in common with the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> than the rest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> lying between them. Both regions are thinly peopled and cling stubbornly to their <a href=\"/index.php/Laws_and_justice_of_the_Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Laws and justice of the Seven Kingdoms\">laws</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Customs\" title=\"Customs\">traditions</a>, and neither was actually conquered by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>. In addition, Brude observed that Dorne and the north are derided as 'savages' by the other five 'civilized' kingdoms.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brude&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403112908\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.247 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 489/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10420/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5281/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 374/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 818/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.44 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  238.331      1 -total\n 97.20%  231.657      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.41%  229.775      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.71%   27.909     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.90%   11.677      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.15%    5.125      2 Template:Ref\n  1.30%    3.108      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.57%    1.347      1 Template:References\n  0.36%    0.847      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>